WEBVTT

00:03.699 --> 00:04.047
.

00:04.091 --> 00:05.875
- Previously
on "Good Girls"...

00:05.918 --> 00:07.007
- So we wanted to talk to you

00:07.050 --> 00:08.573
about doing some
custom work for us.

00:08.617 --> 00:10.184
Casino night!

00:10.227 --> 00:12.316
- If it go into the wrong
hands, it's kind of, like...

00:12.360 --> 00:13.665
counterfeit.
- So you mean, like,

00:13.709 --> 00:15.754
if someone wanted
something special printed,

00:15.798 --> 00:16.842
you would draw it?

00:16.886 --> 00:18.975
What's up, ladies?

00:19.019 --> 00:21.325
- You cannot finish that plate.

00:21.369 --> 00:23.458
- He said he'd let me go--
- He won't!

00:23.501 --> 00:25.155
Wait.
You need us.

00:25.199 --> 00:26.548
You need all of us.

00:26.591 --> 00:27.636
- Not all of you.

00:27.679 --> 00:29.159
[gunshots]

00:29.203 --> 00:31.118
♪

00:31.161 --> 00:33.076
- Hers.
- Oh, oh!

00:33.120 --> 00:34.556
- Take it out,

00:34.599 --> 00:35.905
Elizabeth.

00:35.948 --> 00:38.168
That's what we used
to take care of your friend,

00:38.212 --> 00:40.475
by the way.

00:40.518 --> 00:43.043
- Why?
- Incentive.

00:43.086 --> 00:44.609
- Why did I touch it?

00:44.653 --> 00:46.002
- Why did you touch it?

00:46.046 --> 00:48.700
- What if we pay someone
to blow his brains out?

00:48.744 --> 00:49.745
A professional.

00:49.788 --> 00:50.833
- So how's a lady like you

00:50.876 --> 00:52.617
get involved
with a guy like that?

00:52.661 --> 00:53.836
- I was just bored.

00:53.879 --> 00:55.925
- Third one this month
out of Detroit.

00:55.968 --> 00:57.318
Car paint?

00:57.361 --> 00:59.363
- Or nail polish.
It's a woman.

00:59.407 --> 01:01.626
You know this bitch
is hiding in a cave somewhere.

01:01.670 --> 01:03.193
We just got to root her out.

01:03.237 --> 01:04.760
- Have you guys
seen my phone?

01:04.803 --> 01:06.675
- Is that hers?

01:06.718 --> 01:08.068
- They got nothing
in their bank accounts.

01:08.111 --> 01:09.373
- So?
- They're making

01:09.417 --> 01:10.722
some of the best fake money
I've ever seen.

01:10.766 --> 01:12.028
You don't live a little?

01:12.072 --> 01:13.073
- To hit men.

01:13.116 --> 01:14.596
- Good luck and Godspeed.

01:14.639 --> 01:16.598
- No way!

01:16.641 --> 01:17.903
You did my nails.

01:17.947 --> 01:19.644
- Oh.
Hey.

01:19.688 --> 01:20.906
- So...

01:20.950 --> 01:22.386
what are you guys celebrating?

01:22.430 --> 01:24.562
- You had pizza
with your therapist?

01:24.606 --> 01:26.434
- He's helping me.
It's like a study buddy.

01:26.477 --> 01:28.131
- Before we get started,
I wanted to introduce you

01:28.175 --> 01:29.785
to Lila.
- I'll see you at home.

01:29.828 --> 01:31.178
♪

01:31.221 --> 01:34.311
- I proposed to Lila
a couple nights ago.

01:34.355 --> 01:37.619
- We would like to buy
your place, Gayle.

01:37.662 --> 01:39.273
Where are we gonna get
that kind of money?

01:39.316 --> 01:40.578
- I don't know.

01:40.622 --> 01:42.493
- I just don't want him
involved again.

01:42.537 --> 01:43.494
- Okay.

01:43.538 --> 01:44.452
Hot tubs.

01:44.495 --> 01:46.106
He gets to feel like a man,

01:46.149 --> 01:48.020
and we have a new way
to wash our cut.

01:48.064 --> 01:50.371
- Welcome to Boland Bubbles.

01:50.414 --> 01:51.633
- When does it get to be mine?

01:51.676 --> 01:54.157
