04:02.938 --> 04:05.549
- I'm sorry.

04:05.593 --> 04:08.552
- We were drawing
the SpaceX rocket--

04:08.596 --> 04:10.380
- Mm.
- Oh, well, he loves art.

04:10.424 --> 04:12.904
- He added testicles.

04:16.778 --> 04:19.259
- Don't worry.
