deeper at play.

04:26.396 --> 04:28.093
- What do you mean?

04:28.137 --> 04:31.183
- Have you ever heard of ADHD?

04:31.227 --> 04:33.229
- Okay, hold on a minute.

04:33.273 --> 04:35.275
- Fart putty
is a disorder now?

04:35.318 --> 04:37.451
- Yeah, I mean...
[rapid flatulence]

04:37.494 --> 04:39.975
Stuff's addictive.
[rapid flatulence]

04:40.018 --> 04:42.847
- He treats my classroom like
it's his own YouTube channel.

04:42.891 --> 04:45.110
- Yeah, okay.
But he's not deficient.

04:45.154 --> 04:48.113
- There are 20 other students
that are here to learn.

04:48.157 --> 04:49.506
- He loves it.

04:51.029 --> 04:52.553
- Okay.

04:52.596 --> 04:54.119
If you're not
gonna handle this,

04:54.163 --> 04:57.775
