a different course of action.

04:57.819 --> 04:59.429
- Huh.

04:59.473 --> 05:01.475
- Like what?

05:01.518 --> 05:03.085
Kick him out of school?

05:06.480 --> 05:09.134
- Just have him tested.

05:09.178 --> 05:14.139
- [breathes deeply]

05:14.183 --> 05:15.750
- What about a magician?

05:15.793 --> 05:19.188
- 'Cause I'm turning eight?

05:19.231 --> 05:21.146
- Oh, what about
the bingo hall?

05:21.190 --> 05:23.192
- 'Cause I'm turning 80?

05:23.235 --> 05:25.455
- Fine, well, you tell me.
What do you want to do?

05:25.499 --> 05:26.848
- Nothing.

05:26.891 --> 05:28.110
- Nothing?

05:28.153 --> 05:30.112
We're not gonna
not celebrate your birthday.

05:30.155 --> 05:31.287
- Birthdays are lame.

05:31.331 --> 05:34.725
