06:40.312 --> 06:42.532
- Aha.

06:42.576 --> 06:43.794
- It's mostly me.

06:43.838 --> 06:45.100
- Mm.

06:45.143 --> 06:47.972
- It's 100% me.

06:48.016 --> 06:50.758
