me to realize out loud

06:52.890 --> 06:54.414
that I'm some kind
of narcissist

06:54.457 --> 06:56.894
and I've been ignoring my son?

06:56.938 --> 07:00.420
- The out-loud part
is optional, but...

07:04.075 --> 07:06.426
- Perhaps we could talk
about something else?

07:06.469 --> 07:09.080
- Your time.

07:09.124 --> 07:10.517
- Okay.

07:10.560 --> 07:12.432
What happened to your face?

07:12.475 --> 07:15.086
- I shaved.

07:15.130 --> 07:16.871
- For her?

07:16.914 --> 07:19.047
- For me.

07:19.090 --> 07:21.441
- You picked a date
for the wedding?

07:23.225 --> 07:24.748
- No.

07:25.880 --> 07:28.143
- Venue?

07:28.186 --> 07:29.492
- No.

07:30.624 --> 07:33.104
- Guest list?

07:33.148 --> 07:34.932
- Not yet.

07:34.976 --> 07:37.892
- Am in invited?

07:37.935 --> 07:40.024
- Nope.

07:40.068 --> 07:41.504
- Ouch.

07:43.201 --> 07:45.465
- Would you want to come?

07:45.508 --> 07:47.118
- Nope.

07:48.903 --> 07:50.557
- Ouch.

07:51.732 --> 07:55.213
[breathes deeply]

