Um...

08:05.528 --> 08:08.836
is there anything else
you'd like to cover?

08:13.318 --> 08:15.233
- What day is it today?

08:16.365 --> 08:18.541
- Um...

08:18.585 --> 08:20.500
Tuesday.
- You sure?

08:20.543 --> 08:22.327
- Yeah.

08:22.371 --> 08:23.546
- What was yesterday?

08:25.940 --> 08:28.246
- Monday.
- Tomorrow?

08:30.031 --> 08:31.598
Come on.

08:34.383 --> 08:35.384
- Wednesday.

08:35.427 --> 08:37.473
- Mm.
[chuckles]

08:37.517 --> 08:40.084
So you do understand
the concept of time.

08:40.128 --> 08:42.434
Where my cut at?

08:42.478 --> 08:44.959
- I said we were almost open.

08:45.002 --> 08:46.526
- Mm-hmm.

08:46.569 --> 08:49.137
Kind of like being
almost pregnant, right?

08:49.180 --> 08:51.748
- We have been killing
ourselves

08:51.792 --> 08:54.142
printing money for you
seven days a week.

08:54.185 --> 08:56.231
Don't touch that.
It's still wet.

08:57.798 --> 08:59.582
- It's just a bunch
of pretty paper.

08:59.626 --> 09:01.018
- You know,
you can't just start

09:01.062 --> 09:02.585
selling hot tubs willy-nilly.

09:02.629 --> 09:03.804
