09:03.847 --> 09:06.850
- And that's not your problem.

09:06.894 --> 09:09.200
- Well, then
what is my problem?

09:09.244 --> 09:10.985
[dramatic music]

09:11.028 --> 09:12.769
- It's the school carnival.

09:12.813 --> 09:14.858
♪

09:14.902 --> 09:17.992
- Uh, okay.
I'll make cookies.

09:18.035 --> 09:19.384
- Oh, um...

09:19.428 --> 09:24.128
so we were thinking
more, like, mini Khanom Chans.

09:24.172 --> 09:25.565
- What's that?

09:25.608 --> 09:27.567
- The traditional Thai dessert?

09:27.610 --> 09:29.046
- "Chan" means "layer."

09:29.090 --> 09:30.134
- Why?

09:30.178 --> 09:31.309
- To go with
the fundraising theme.

09:31.353 --> 09:32.528
- "One Night in Bangkok."

09:32.572 --> 09:34.269
- It'll be so cute
with the song playing

09:34.312 --> 09:36.184
